EM_0021|Cu-64|Which major emission is correct?|Mixed decay: positron emission, beta-minus emission, and electron capture|Cu-64 has a mixed decay profile including positron emission, beta-minus emission, and electron capture. This makes it interesting for theranostic applications.|3|mixed_beta_plus_beta_minus_ec